        "en.hubeali": [
          "<a id=\"_Toc492473259\">H 14588</a> – From him, from Ahmad, from Ali Bin Hadeed, from some of our companions, who has narrated the following:",
          "<span class=\"first-chapter-phrase\"><span class=\"first-in-chapter character-a\">A</span>bu Abdullah</span><sup>asws</sup> said: ‘It is inherent in the hearts to love the one who benefits it, and hate the one who harms it’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "140. From him, from Ahmad, from Ali Bin Hadeed, from some of our companions, who has narrated the following: Abu Abdullah (a.s.) said: ‘It is inherent in the hearts to love the one who benefits it, and hate the one who harms it’."
        ]
